T1  - Give Me Your Tired, Your Poor, Your High-Skilled Labor: H-1B Lottery Outcomes and Entrepreneurial Success
AU  - Dimmock, Stephen G.
AU  - Huang, Jiekun
AU  - Weisbenner, Scott J.
Y1  - 2021/11/05
PY  - 2021
